snippet: After being pulled on its first day of release, the film “Django Unchained” is likely to undergo slight cuts for the Chinese market.
abstract: Quentin Tarantino film Django Unchained is expected to return to theaters in China after further editing.
lead_paragraph: After being pulled on its first day of release, the film “Django Unchained” is likely to undergo slight cuts for the Chinese market.

headline.main: China’s Theaters May Soon Show Tarantino Film
